  <title>Week 1 day 3</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>Today we will discuss automation vs autonomy for robots, and will work on controlling our robot movements more.</p>
  </introduction>
  <paragraphs>
    <title>Lab</title>
    <p>Look at <xref ref="sec-lab-controlled-movement"/></p>
