  <paragraphs>
    <title>Notes</title>
    <p>Link to the notes on <url href="https://hackmd.io/@skiadas/ryPAVlfLc">automation vs autonomy</url>.</p>
    <p>
      Questions:
      <ul>
        <li>Would non-deterministic robots be safe in critical environments?</li>
        <li>Confused about open world vs closed world</li>
        <li>What other sensors will we have available?</li>
        <li>How much autonomy is actually helpful (before we lose trust)?</li>
        <li>How is it possible to evaluate mistakes in an autonomous system?</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </paragraphs>
  <paragraphs>
    <title>Reading</title>
